To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ThreeWhiteSoldiers _threewhitesoldiers;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_threewhitesoldiers = ThreeWhiteSoldiers(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_threewhitesoldiers.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "threewhitesoldiers", _threewhitesoldiers.Current.Value);
}
